name: Moon
description:
Although the moon is not a planet, it is the destinations that most artists prefer.
Poets, singers, actors, and others have already ascended to the moon in a way 
that only art can do.
-----------
"Moon"  is the seventh and last, one of a kind, destination piece of a celestial eptalogy.
